title: Help me my model does not appear in gzweb

content.raw:
I am working with ros kinetic and gzweb.

My model launches with no error \(picture rosl\_SS.png\) besides gzweb shows my world but not shows my model\(picture gzweb\_SS.png \).

On the other hand if i change the my model dae file my models some parts appears in gzweb. I think some dae file blocks other dae file for example: when i use base.dae file my tire is not appear if i use tire.dae wheel is not appear.

I hope i could tell my problem clearly.
content.html:
I am working with ros kinetic and gzweb.

My model launches with no error (picture rosl_SS.png) besides gzweb shows my world but not shows my model(picture gzweb_SS.png ).

On the other hand if i change the my model dae file my models some parts appears in gzweb. I think some dae file blocks other dae file for example: when i use base.dae file my tire is not appear if i use tire.dae wheel is not appear.

I hope i could tell my problem clearly.
